{{linkless|October 2006}} 
[[Image:ElishaShapiro.jpg|thumb|right|''Vote Nihilist 2006'' campaign publicity photo]]

'''Elisha Shapiro''' is an [[United States|American]] [[nihilism|nihilist]] known for his creation of public spectacles promoting a philosophical rejection of objective value and [[truth]]. [[As of 2006]], Shapiro is running as an [[independent (politician)|independent]] in the [[Governor of California]] election. His platform includes [[Free education|free college education]], [[secession]] from the United States and [[same-sex marriage|marriage for gays]] only.<ref>[http://www.vcreporter.com/article.php?id=3549&IssueNum=79 Nihilist for California Governor?], via [[VCReporter]]</ref>

